     | Add Todo(녹바탕) |
      ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
페이지를 새로고침해 보면, 이렇게 Home 링크와 Todos 링크, Logout 링크가 있다 

Whitelabel Error Page
This application has no explicit mapping for /error, so you are seeing this as a fallback.

Fri May 03 17:11:22 KST 2024
There was an unexpected error (type=Not Found, status=404).
No static resource .
org.springframework.web.servlet.resource.NoResourceFoundException: No static resource .
	at 

지금은 Home 링크가 작동하지 않는 걸 볼 수 있고 Logout 링크도 작동하지 않는 걸 볼 것이다
그것도 수정할 것이다, 여기서 지금 작동하는 유일한 링크는 Todos 링크다, Todos를 누르면 이 링크로 오고


너가 Add Todo를 클릭하면 todo.jsp로 오게 되는데
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

http://localhost:8087/add-todo 페이지 화면 ==>


      Enter Todo Details
                    _______________________   
      Description  |                       |     
                    ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾   
                    _______________________   
      Target Date  |2025-05-03             |     
                    ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾   

       ________     
      | 제  출 |
       ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

그럼 이걸 todo.jsp에도 추가해보겠다

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


⏺ todo.jsp 파일


<%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core"%>
<%@ taglib prefix="form" uri="http://www.springframework.org/tags/form"%>

<html>
<head>
<link href="webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="webjars/bootstrap-datepicker/1.9.0/css/bootstrap-datepicker.standalone.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<title>Add Todo Page</title>
</head>

    <!--2: 그럼 todo.jsp에서도 여기에 nav를 추가하려 한다고 해줄 수 있다 그리고 새로 고침 하면..-->
		<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-light bg-light mb-3 p-1">
			<a class="navbar-brand m-1" href="https://courses.in28minutes.com">in28Minutes</a>
			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
				<ul class="navbar-nav">
					<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
					<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/list-todos">Todos</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<ul class="navbar-nav">
				<li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>

<body>
	<!-- <div>Welcome to in28minutes</div> -->
	<div class="container">

		<h1>Enter Todo Details</h1>
		<form:form method="post" modelAttribute="todo">
			<fieldset class="mb-3">
				<form:label path="description">Description</form:label>
				<form:input type="text" path="description" required="required" />
				<form:errors path="description" cssClass="text-warning" />
			</fieldset>

			<fieldset class="mb-3">
				<form:label path="targetDate">Target Date</form:label>
				<form:input type="text" path="targetDate" required="required" />
				<form:errors path="targetDate" cssClass="text-warning" />
			</fieldset>

			<form:input type="hidden" path="id" />
			<form:input type="hidden" path="done" />
			<input type="submit" class="btn btn-success" />

		</form:form>

	</div>
	<script src="webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<script src="webjars/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="webjars/bootstrap-datepicker/1.9.0/js/bootstrap-datepicker.min.js"></script>	
	<script type="text/javascript">
	$('#targetDate').datepicker({
	    format: 'yyyy-mm-dd'
	});
	</script>
	
</body>
</html>

